~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : outphr                                    ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : outphr [<message>]

   This sets the message that is displayed following your name 
   when you leave a room. eg if your name is fred and you set it 
   to "leaves fast" other people will see "Fred leaves fast" when 
   you leave a room. If you omit the message it shows you your 
   current message.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : inphr, desc, set
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
